Class UdpMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.illinois.mitra.starl.comms.UdpMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Traceable

    public class UdpMessage
extends java.lang.Object
implements Traceable
    UDPMessage is a wrapper for RobotMessage which includes additional information to track acknowledgments. This is used only by low level message handling and shouldn't be needed by StarL applications
